44
00:03:51,540 --> 00:03:56,989
This is a signal that the prices need to come
down in order to increase the quantity demanded,

45
00:03:56,990 --> 00:04:02,750
and decrease the quantity supplied. When will
the price stop falling? When the surplus goes

46
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:07,870
away, the downward pressure eases. This means
that when the quantity supplied equals the

47
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:12,400
quantity demanded, at P1, the market stabilizes.

48
